These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-1::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, tulip
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, july, october
3 different games are played: go, canasta, snooker
3 different pets are kept: frog, turtle, guinea-pig
 1. the owner of the frog and the person who's birthday is in july have different parity positions##9
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 3. the owner of the frog is not the person who growsballoon-flower##6
 4. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in april and the person who growsballoon-flower have different parity positions##9
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growstulip##1
 7. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
 8. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july and the person who growstulip have different parity positions##9
10. the person playing go is the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Job           | lily | balloon-flower | tulip    |
| Music-Genre   | april       | july   | october   |
| Nationality   | canasta    | go | snooker  |
| Transport     | guinea-pig   | turtle       | frog |

