.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-2::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, rugby, skiing
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, turquise
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, pall-mall, alhambra
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, lily
1. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
2. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##8
3. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5
4. the havana-smoker and the person who's sport is rugby have the same parity positions##9
5. the person who likes apricot and the person who's sport is climbing have different parity positions##9
6. the person who likes turquise is in the middle##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who likes ivory##3
8. the alhambra-smoker is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3     |
| Food          | skiing  | climbing         | rugby |
| Hobby         | apricot | turquise | ivory   |
| Movie-Genre   | pall-mall     | alhambra       | havana     |
| Transport     | zinnia       | amaryllis          | lily    |

