.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-9-3::.
3 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, whist
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, victorian
City: edinburgh, miami, new-york
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, january, december
1. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
2. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
3. the person playing whist is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
5. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the person traveling to miami##8
8. the person playing poker and the person traveling to new-york have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | poker | mah-jongg | whist |
| Movie-Genre   | victorian      | gothic-revival   | cape-cod  |
| Music-Genre   | new-york        | edinburgh  | miami         |
| Transport     | december       | april    | january       |

