There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, milk
1. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
3. the nigerian and the person eating cauliflower have different parity positions##9
4. the argentine is in the middle##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
6. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
7. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
8. the argentine is not to the right of the person eating pepper##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |       3       |
| Job           | corn    | cauliflower | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | nigerian | argentine       | chinese     |
| Pet           | surfing        | skateboarding      | snowboarding          |
| Transport     | coffee        | milk         | 7up     |

