3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, prince, davidoff
3 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, fish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, marigold, sunflower
1. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
3. the person who growssunflower is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who growszinnia##2
4. the person who growsmarigold is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
5. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who growsmarigold have the same parity positions##9
6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
7. the prince-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
8. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
9. the owner of the fish is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Hobby         | water  | 7up   | almond-milk |
| Job           | prince   | davidoff | aristoff |
| Movie-Genre   | fish   | rabbit  | mouse     |
| Nationality   | zinnia | sunflower    | marigold  |

